targets.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
targets.query:
$columns(
    'PSR %sat %freq',
    avg(psr) psr)
FROM $table
WHERE
    sat = '$satgraph'
    AND freq IN ($freq)
targets.rawQuery: SELECT t, groupArray((concat('PSR ', sat, ' ', freq), psr)) as groupArr FROM ( SELECT intDiv(time, 500) * 500 as t, sat, freq, avg(psr) psr FROM rawdata.range WHERE d BETWEEN toDate(1595878988378/1000) AND toDate(1595879279537/1000) AND time BETWEEN 1595878988378 AND 1595879279537 AND      sat = 'GPS30'     AND freq IN ('L1CA') GROUP BY t, sat, freq  ORDER BY t, sat, freq) GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
